Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1440674,1443219}Sunday, May 21.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1443219,1448349}Paris is full of life, and the faces of people\Nare brightened by long-forgotten smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1449058,1453145}Between one fight and another, the streets\Nof the city host lively dance parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.89,0:24:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1453896,1457108}Fireworks explode against\Na clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1457108,1459819}For the first time in a long time,\Nthe people of Paris enjoy alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.82,0:24:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1460820,1462530}However…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.53,0:24:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1462530,1464365}Next time on "Isabelle from Paris":
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.36,0:24:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1464365,1467284}"Midday Dance Party".\NPlease look forward to it.
