Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.34,0:24:53.35,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1487346,1493352}Your smile is so nice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.35,0:24:58.64,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1493352,1498649}It displays so much love,\Ngentle like a breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.64,0:25:03.65,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1498649,1503654}La la la, our song\Nreaches across the stream
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.65,0:25:08.78,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1503654,1508784}and echoes in the green mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.78,0:25:14.12,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1508784,1514123}Let's run with all our might
